headline: Arizona utilities sign up for gas pipeline project, spurred by data center development
summary: Arizona Public Service has 4.5 GW of committed large load in its interconnection queue and 20 GW of other potential large customers, Pinnacle West CEO Ted Geisler said Wednesday.
